# Input

```grit
`var $x = [$names]` => `var coolPeople = [$names]` where {
  $names <: every or {`"andrew"`, `"alex"`},
	$names <: not contains `"sam"`
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
`var $x = [$names]` => `var coolPeople = [$names]` where {
	$names <: every or {
		`"andrew"`,
		`"alex"`
	},
	$names <: not contains `"sam"`
}

```
